name: subw_upper_flag
details: `width_fitb` and `logsubw_int_rest` indicate upper limits if 1. Otherwise 0. Different for sub-bursts.

name: scat_upper_flag
details: `scat_time` indicates the upper limit if 1. Otherwise 0. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: spec_z
details: spectroscopic redshift if available. Otherwise -9999. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: spec_z_flag
details: spec z is available if 1. Otherwise 0. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: E_obs
details: (Jy ms Hz): fluence (Jy ms) × delta_v, where delta_v is the band width of 400 MHz at observer's frame. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: E_obs_error
details: (Jy ms Hz): error of E obs. Common for subbursts with the same tns name.

name: subb_flag
details: 1 if the row belongs to multiple sub-bursts. 0 means FRBs without sub-bursts. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: subb_p_flag
details: subb p flag=1 can be used when sub-burst parameters are used. All rows have 1.

name: common_p_flag
details: common p flag=1 can be used when common parameters are used. For each tns name, the first sub-burst indicates 1. Different for sub-bursts.

name: delta_nuo_FRB
details: (MHz) observed spectral band width. Common for sub-bursts. i.e. high freq-low freq for FRBs without multiple sub-bursts and max(high freq)-min(low freq) for FRBs with multiple sub-bursts. The latter works because there is no frequency gap between sub-bursts in the catalogue.

name: z_DM
details: redshift derived from a dispersion measure. 50 percentile of the probability distribution function (PDF). Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: z_DM_error_p
details: +1σ of z DM. 84.135 percentile of the PDF - z_DM. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: z_DM_error_m
details: -1σ of z DM. z_DM - 15.865 percentile of the PDF. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: E_obs_400
details: (Jy ms Hz): observed energy integrated over 400 MHz at emitter's frame. 50 percentile of the PDF. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: E_obs_400_error_p
details: (Jy ms Hz): +1σ of E obs 400. 84.135 percentile of the PDF - E_obs_400. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: E_obs_400_error_m
details: (Jy ms Hz): −1σ of E obs 400. E obs 400 - 15.865 percentile of the PDF. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: logsubw_int_rest
details: (ms) log rest-frame intrinsic duration of a sub-burst in the logarithmic scale. 50 percentile of the PDF. Different for sub-bursts.

name: logsubw_int_rest_error_p
details: (ms) +1σ of logsubw int rest. 84.135 percentile of the PDF - subw int rest. Different for subbursts.

name: logsubw_int_rest_error_m
details: (ms) −1σ of logsubw int rest. logsubw int rest - 15.865 percentile of the PDF. Different for subbursts.

name: z
details: spec_z if available, otherwise z DM. Common for subbursts with the same tns name.

name: z_error_p
details: spec z error if spec z is available, otherwise z_DM_error_p. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: z_error_m
details: spec z error if spec z is available, otherwise z DM_error_m. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: logE_rest_400
details: (erg) radio energy in the logarithmic scale integrated over 400 MHz at emitter's frame. 50 percentile of the PDF. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: logE_rest_400_error_p
details: (erg) +1σ of logE rest 400. 84.135 percentile of the PDF - logE rest 400. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: logE_rest_400_error_m
details: (erg) -1σ of logE rest 400. logE rest 400 -15.865 percentile of the PDF. Common for subbursts with the same tns name.

name: logrhoA
details: (Gpc^-3 yr^-1) the number density in the logarithmic scale derived by the Vmax method and redshift bin A. Uncorrected for the selection functions. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: logrhoA_error_p
details: (Gpc^-3 yr^-1) +1σ of logrhoA. 84.135 percentile of the PDF - logrhoA. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: logrhoA_error_m
details: (Gpc^-3 yr^-1) -1σ of logrhoA. logrhoA - 15.865 percentile of the PDF. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: logrhoB
details: (Gpc^-3 yr^-1) the number density in the logarithmic scale derived by the Vmax method and redshift bin B. Uncorrected for the selection functions. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: logrhoB_error_p
details: (Gpc^-3 yr^-1) +1σ of logrhoB. 84.135 percentile of the PDF - logrhoB. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: logrhoB_error_m
details: (Gpc^-3 yr^-1) -1σ of logrhoB. logrhoB - 15.865 percentile of the PDF. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: weight_DM
details: weight factor of DMobs. Common for subbursts with the same tns name.

name: weight_DM_error_p
details: +1σ of weight DM. 84.135 percentile of the PDF - weight DM. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: weight_DM_error_m
details: -1σ of weight DM. weight DM -15.865 percentile of the PDF. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: weight_scat
details: weight factor of τ_scat. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: weight_scat_error_p
details: +1σ of weight scat. 84.135 percentile of the PDF - weight scat. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: weight_scat_error_m
details: -1σ of weight scat. weight scat -15.865 percentile of the PDF. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: weight_w_int
details: weight factor of w_int. Common for subbursts with the same tns name.

name: weight_w_int_error_p
details: +1σ of weight w int. 84.135 percentile of the PDF - weight w int. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: weight_w_int_error_m
details: -1σ of weight w int. weight w int -15.865 percentile of the PDF. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: weight_fluence
details: weight factor of fluence. Common for subbursts with the same tns name.

name: weight_fluence_error_p
details: +1σ of weight fluence. 84.135 percentile of the PDF - weight fluence. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: weight_fluence_error_m
details: -1σ of weight fluence. weight fluence -15.865 percentile of the PDF. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: weight
details: weight DM×weight scat×weight w int×weight fluence. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: weight_error_p
details: +1σ of weight. 84.135 percentile of the PDF - weight. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: weight_error_m
details: -1σ of weight. weight -15.865 percentile of the PDF. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: weighted_logrhoA
details: (Gpc^-3 yr^-1) the number density in the logarithmic scale (redshift bin A) corrected for the selection functions. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: weighted_logrhoA_error_p
details: (Gpc^-3 yr^-1) +1σ of weighted logrhoA. 84.135 percentile of the PDF - weighted logrhoA. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: weighted_logrhoA_error_m
details: (Gpc^-3 yr^-1) -1σ of weighted logrhoA. weighted logrhoA -15.865 percentile of the PDF. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: weighted_logrhoB
details: (Gpc^-3 yr^-1) the number density in the logarithmic scale (redshift bin A) corrected for the selection functions. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: weighted_logrhoB_error_p
details: (Gpc^-3 yr^-1) +1σ of weighted logrhoB. 84.135 percentile of the PDF - weighted logrhoB. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.

name: weighted_logrhoB_error_m
details: (Gpc^-3 yr^-1) -1σ of weighted logrhoB. weighted logrhoB -15.865 percentile of the PDF. Common for sub-bursts with the same tns name.
